*Položaj* mu je bio nezavidan. (His position was enviable.)
Njegov *položaj* u društvu bio je vrlo važan. (His position in society was very important.)
Bila je u nezavidnom *položaju*. (She was in an unenviable position.)
Ona je pokušala da promeni svoj *položaj*. (She tried to change her position.)
Njegov *položaj* je nepovoljan. (His position is unfavorable.)